839
01:08:10,886 --> 01:08:13,720
<i>...que Lucy consiguiera esto.</i>

840
01:08:14,456 --> 01:08:18,950
<i>Es tan perfecto.</i>

841
01:08:45,888 --> 01:08:48,015
